title: What is Love?
author: hayley
text: what is love?  when you love someone who loves you back,  what does it feel like? when you are betrayed by someone that you love,  how do you feel? when you love someone who loves you back you feel appreiciated and cared for.  you feel grateful for everything the person you love has done for you.  when you are betrayed by someone that you love you feel rejected and disapointed.  you feel like you can not trust that person any more and you feel like you can not love them any longer.  love is fate and nothing more.  love will never be a mistake.  you can fall into love,  but. . .  you can not fall out of love.  if you fall out of love you did not love in the first place.  love is delicate and has a bond to bring two people together.  if two people do love eachother truly then the bond can not be broken.  if two people do not love eachother,  they did  not love in the first place.  love is strong and can last forever,  yet. . .  love is complicated.  love is like a rollercoaster.  love has its ups and downs.  to love you have to be dedicated. . .  to the person you love,  and you have to be willing. . .  to contribute your lives to love,  otherwise. . .  what is love?
